  "title": "Service Staff",
  "description": "<ul><li><strong>Job Description and Requirements:</strong></li><li> Welcoming guests, answering menu questions, making recommendations, and addressing complaints.</li><li> Taking orders accurately, using POS systems, and relaying information to kitchen/bar staff.</li><li>Serving food and beverages, refilling drinks, and clearing tables (pre-bussing).</li><li> Preparing tables with cutlery/napkins, cleaning dining areas, and adhering to sanitation standards.</li><li> Handling cash or digital payments, providing change, and ensuring accurate billing. </li></ul><p><strong>Key Requirements and Skills</strong><br /></p><ul><li> Proven experience as a waiter or in a customer-facing role is often required.</li><li> Familiarity with Point of Sale (POS) systems, restaurant software, and food safety regulations.</li><li> Ability to stand and walk for long periods and lift trays up to 10-15kg.</li><li> Strong communication, multitasking, active listening, and conflict-resolution skills.</li><li> Ability to work shifts, including weekends, evenings, and holidays. </li></ul>",
